OL,3,CInsurers charging rates similar to
OL,4,Ccredit cards for monthly cover ` Which?
OL,6,FSome motorists could be charged nearly
OL,7,F40% APR (annual percentage rate) when
OL,8,Fpaying for their insurance monthly,
OL,9,Faccording to Which?
OL,11,FAnd some home insurers are charging
OL,12,Fnearly 35% APR on monthly payments,
OL,13,Fthe consumer group said.
OL,15,FIt added that the rates being charged
OL,16,Fby some insurers to pay for monthly
OL,17,Fcover resemble the interest applicable
OL,18,Ffor credit card borrowing.
