OL,3,CInsurers charging rates similar to
OL,4,Ccredit cards for monthly cover ` Which?
OL,6,FWhich? asked 39 car insurers and 34
OL,7,Fhome insurers what APRs were being
OL,8,Fapplied to monthly payments.
OL,10,FMany insurers did not disclose their
OL,11,FAPR. Among those that did, Which?
OL,12,Ffound that 1st Central charges between
OL,13,F5% and 39.11%. It gives customers a
OL,14,Fpersonal interest rate after a credit
OL,15,Frisk assessment, Which? said.
OL,17,FThe average rate across 27 providers
OL,18,Fthat charge interest and disclosed
OL,19,Ftheir rate was 23.37%.
