OL,4,Ccredit cards for monthly cover ` Which?
OL,6,FOnly two car insurers asked ` NFU
OL,7,FMutual and Hiscox ` said they do not
OL,8,Fcharge interest on monthly repayments.
OL,10,F1st Central told Which?: "We
OL,11,Funderstand it is important to
OL,12,Fcustomers that we keep the price of
OL,13,Finsurance as low as possible ` and
OL,14,Fbenchmarking tells us that we are
OL,15,Fcompetitive for both annual premiums
OL,16,Fand for those that wish to pay monthly
OL,17,Fthrough a credit arrangement.
