OL,6,FFifteen home insurance providers
OL,7,Fsurveyed said they do not charge
OL,8,Finterest: Bank of Scotland, Halifax,
OL,9,FHiscox, HSBC, Lloyds Bank, MBNA, M&S
OL,10,FBank, Nationwide Building Society, NFU
OL,11,FMutual, SAGIC, Sainsbury's Bank,
OL,12,FSantander, TSB, Urban Jungle and
OL,13,FYorkshire Building Society.
OL,15,FWhich? said that, in January this
OL,16,Fyear, the average credit card rate was
OL,17,F34.8% with the majority of cards
OL,18,Fcharging up to 25%.
