OL,6,FWhich? said the regulator should
OL,7,Fproduce an action plan to make sure
OL,8,Fthat firms are providing fair value in
OL,9,Fthe interest rates they are charging
OL,10,Fcustomers. It called for a league
OL,11,Ftable of providers to be produced by
OL,12,Fthe regulator.
OL,14,FRocio Concha, Which? director of
OL,15,Fpolicy and advocacy, said the FCA
OL,16,Fshould "step up and to get tough with
OL,17,Ffirms".
